However as she grows up and matures, our relationship is becoming increasingly open and candid, although I doubt that it will ever be on the level of a best friend in terms of confidences, but will always be a longlasting one. Her focus on goals and her poise and ability to stay focused is excellent. Her energy level of good although sometimes she does not want to put out the effort (including effort to overcome unease) to get something that in fact she values; this is especially true with personal and professional relationships. ",Unknown
